{"tid":752875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發癲亂咬] 指李慧玲涉誹謗 梁振英:有依法保護聲譽權利","createTime":"2018-07-23T07:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T00:34:48.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93abfbff743eae45f4c29fc916b9b888add767ca","tid":752875,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"網絡電台D100節目主持人李慧玲日前表示收到政協副主席、前特首梁振英發出的律師信，指她在節目中有誹謗之嫌，要求道歉。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英今早於facebook回應事件，指古今中外皆有誹謗法，法律面前人人平等，官員有依法保護自己和家人聲譽的權利。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英指出，李慧玲在6月28日的《左右大局》由於揑造事實，觸犯民事和刑事誹謗，要求其更正和道歉，不過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>梁振英並未提及涉及誹謗的內容</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又提及會計界立法會議員梁繼昌於16個月前，指他當時被香港和外國稅局調査中，不宜任全國政協副主席，梁振英重申他從來沒有收過任何稅局的査詢。"},{"pid":"179dbd184b480ed5668a0fc7bc67396033195a17","tid":752875,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我9錢一撚早屌過：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共狗先係至大資本玩家，至叻利用但不尊守西方人法價值作政治武器！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ee80bb047baa1ace2e53e80b84ba34f78c248894","tid":752875,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咬你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}